Coming Soon to Forbidden: The ZOMBS

An efficient solution for making zombies in Roblox.
Includes A* pathfinding logic, precomputed pathing, anti-stuck logic, etc...

Lite:
> Basic pathfinding
> Soft-coded limit of zombies per instance (soft-coded as performance limitations from the variant of the module do not allow for )


Full Version ($5 USD / 500 robux)
> Support
> Target NPCs
> Anti-Stuck
> Wave Assist
]]--]]></ProtectedString>
